OL,3,CCharity warns of 'disaster' as
OL,4,Chomeless centres close
OL,6,FThe closure of two Birmingham homeless
OL,7,Fcentres has caused uncertainty over
OL,8,Fwho will sleep where this winter, as
OL,9,FLaurence Griffin, ITV Central
OL,10,FProduction Journalist reports.
OL,12,FA former rough sleeper has warned
OL,13,Fpeople experiencing homelessness in
OL,14,FBirmingham could die as two homeless
OL,15,Fshelters providing over 170 beds
OL,16,Fcombined are closing.
