OL,3,CCharity warns of 'disaster' as
OL,4,Chomeless centres close
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council says it made
OL,7,Fthe decision to close Washington Court
OL,8,F- which provides 101 beds - and the
OL,9,FWilliam Booth Centre - which provides
OL,10,Fjust over 70 - as part of a plan to
OL,11,Fchange the way homeless people can
OL,12,Faccess support.
OL,14,FBill West volunteers at Birmingham
OL,15,FCity Mission which provides food and a
OL,16,Fwarm space for people experiencing
OL,17,Fhomelessness, but has used both
OL,18,Fcentres in the past.
