OL,3,CCharity warns of 'disaster' as
OL,4,Chomeless centres close
OL,6,FHe said: "This is going to be a
OL,7,Fdisaster, if we're losing these
OL,8,Fhostels.
OL,10,F"I know what's going to happen now,
OL,11,Fwe're just going to have death rates
OL,12,Fgo up through the winter.
OL,14,F"I ended up with nothing and if it
OL,15,Fwasn't for the Salvation Army and
OL,16,FWashington Court I would have been on
OL,17,Fthe streets, and probably would have
OL,18,Fdied on the streets."
