OL,3,CCharity warns of 'disaster' as
OL,4,Chomeless centres close
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council says it
OL,7,Fremains committed to ensuring there
OL,8,Fare enough beds for people who need
OL,9,Fthem, and the closures are a part of a
OL,10,Fmove from large city centre centres to
OL,11,Fseveral smaller shelters across the
OL,12,Fcity.
OL,14,FPhil Ansell, Birmingham City Mission
OL,15,FManager, said people affected by the
OL,16,Fclosures are "feeling really quite
OL,17,Fanxious at the moment.
