OL,3,CCharity warns of 'disaster' as
OL,4,Chomeless centres close
OL,6,F"They've lived in a place that they
OL,7,Ffelt is safe and warm etc and now
OL,8,Fthey're just feeling as if that maybe
OL,9,Fis taken away from them and there's a
OL,10,Fgreat deal of uncertainty as to their
OL,11,Ffuture."
