OL,3,CCharity warns of 'disaster' as
OL,4,Chomeless centres close
OL,6,FDavid Watson, Head of Support at
OL,7,FTrident Group, which operated the
OL,8,FWashington Court centre said smaller
OL,9,Fcentres are often safer and more
OL,10,Fsupportive environments compared to
OL,11,Flarge city centre homeless shelters.
OL,13,FHe said: "If you've become homeless,
OL,14,Fyou're struggling, you've got an
OL,15,Faddiction problem or you've got a
OL,16,Fmental health issue, the last thing
OL,17,Fthat you want is to be around 100
OL,18,Fpeople who are in just the same boat
OL,19,Fas you.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
